Here's the ChucK program to generate a one-second triangle wave at middle C (C4) and send it to the DAC:

```chuck
// Create the triangle wave oscillator at middle C (261.63 Hz) for 1 second
Tri osc = Tri(261.63, 1.0);
osc => dac;
```

